00:00:47.023 --> 00:00:47.887
=Episode 2=
(Shen Changning died from poisoning?)

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:53.479
Your Lordship.

00:00:54.039 --> 00:00:55.159
These two are too stubborn,

00:00:55.479 --> 00:00:56.399
and won't say a thing.

00:01:00.280 --> 00:01:01.039
Pei Yu.

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.039
You slaughter the innocent

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:04.560
and harm the loyal!

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:06.640
You destroyed the Shen family.

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.560
You will face retribution
sooner or later

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:10.879
and never to rise again!

00:01:11.079 --> 00:01:11.840
Usually,

00:01:12.439 --> 00:01:14.079
you coroners use these things

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:16.200
to make the dead speak.

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:18.280
Today I will use them on you.

00:01:18.599 --> 00:01:19.480
Will what I get

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:20.879
be true

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:22.599
or false?

00:01:22.959 --> 00:01:23.640
Pei Yu.

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:25.439
You are nothing but a dog.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:26.840
Your sister

00:01:27.239 --> 00:01:29.400
learned to serve others

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.400
on a man's bed.

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:41.959
Don't worry.

00:01:43.599 --> 00:01:45.640
I won't let you die easily.

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:49.519
I will

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:55.560
slice you apart piece by piece.

00:01:57.319 --> 00:01:57.879
I'll confess.

00:01:58.460 --> 00:01:59.439
I'll tell you everything!

00:02:02.120 --> 00:02:02.690
Your Lordship.

00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:04.519
The coroner has confirmed that

00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:07.400
the eldest daughter of the Shen family
was poisoned first, then drowned.

00:02:07.879 --> 00:02:09.360
Clearly someone did it deliberately.

00:02:10.159 --> 00:02:11.240
But Your Lordship,

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:13.960
why are you so affected
by Shen Changning's death?

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:29.159
(Pei Yu's sister, Pei Shu)
Help me lift him up.

00:02:30.725 --> 00:02:34.100
(Young Pei Yu)

00:02:38.639 --> 00:02:40.400
(Young Shen Changning)
(Seeing her was when I first believed)

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:43.400
(that a person's eyes could truly)

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:47.360
(shine as bright as the stars.)

00:03:03.759 --> 00:03:05.400
Please accept this half jade pendant

00:03:05.719 --> 00:03:06.479
for saving my life.

00:03:06.700 --> 00:03:07.960
I will repay this debt one day.

00:03:09.879 --> 00:03:11.000
I'll take it then.

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.400
You owe me nothing now.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.159
Just focus on recovering.

00:03:15.639 --> 00:03:16.680
Don't think too much.

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:20.400
May I ask your name, Miss?

00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:24.800
If fate wills it, we'll meet again.

00:03:31.439 --> 00:03:32.719
(Later, I searched for years,)

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:35.400
(only to learn she was
the Shen family's eldest daughter.)

00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:38.199
(I never thought
that when we met again,)

00:03:38.199 --> 00:03:39.900
(we would be separated
by life and death.)

00:03:41.719 --> 00:03:43.319
(I must find her true murderer.)

00:03:47.039 --> 00:03:48.680
What's more, fate played its tricks.

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:51.520
The Shen family fell to ruin

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.879
in my hands.

00:03:59.575 --> 00:04:00.900
(Pei Yu's confidant, Qin Feng)

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.199
This poison is one of the foreign realm's
rare toxins.

00:04:05.439 --> 00:04:05.960
It is pollen,

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:06.759
and also poison.

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:08.120
Ten days ago,

00:04:08.599 --> 00:04:10.199
it appeared at the Xichun House.

00:04:11.759 --> 00:04:12.879
Xichun House.

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:13.919
Xi Yan.

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:18.279
I thought Xiao Huaijin sent Xi Yan

00:04:18.759 --> 00:04:21.079
into the residence to plant a spy.

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.040
But now it seems

00:04:25.480 --> 00:04:26.759
like is not that simple.

00:04:29.439 --> 00:04:30.279
I believe

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:33.360
Xi Yan has always kept quiet
in the backyard,

00:04:33.959 --> 00:04:35.360
but now she has caused such chaos.

00:04:35.700 --> 00:04:36.959
She must have a bigger purpose.

00:04:38.210 --> 00:04:40.200
Why not eliminate her completely,
Your Lordship?

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.399
(Shen Changning's death)

00:04:43.279 --> 00:04:44.800
(is undoubtedly connected to her.)

00:04:52.600 --> 00:04:54.279
(Pei Yu's martial skills
are exceptional.)

00:04:55.319 --> 00:04:57.120
(Only with a single sure strike)

00:04:57.879 --> 00:04:59.040
(can I take his life.)

00:05:00.879 --> 00:05:03.319
(Otherwise, I will only doom myself.)

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.279
(Just as Xiao Huaijin)

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:09.040
(ordered me to cooperate internally.)

00:05:09.839 --> 00:05:12.800
(Using talismans to frame Pei Yu
for plotting against the Emperor.)

00:05:14.279 --> 00:05:16.879
(I might as well go along with it.)

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:19.560
(First, borrow Pei Yu's hand)

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:21.120
(to deal with my other enemies.)

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:24.759
(When they kill each other,)

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:26.639
(I can)

00:05:27.040 --> 00:05:28.839
(reap the profits as the fisherman.)

00:05:30.112 --> 00:05:33.137
♪The flowing years pass
through desolation♪

00:05:33.525 --> 00:05:36.165
♪Unwilling to forgive past mistakes♪

00:05:36.787 --> 00:05:42.662
♪Blaming myself for not protecting
