♪Counting it carefully♪

00:05:46.948 --> 00:05:49.580
♪Who stayed by my side through hardship♪

00:05:49.975 --> 00:05:52.200
♪There will eventually be a pure land♪

00:05:52.337 --> 00:05:56.125
♪Where all karmic burden is cast away♪

00:05:56.660 --> 00:05:59.260
♪Not until worldly splendor fades♪

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:02.840
♪Can one understand
what cuts to the bone♪

00:06:03.900 --> 00:06:05.599
♪At dusk, with white hair♪

00:06:05.623 --> 00:06:09.445
♪I still cannot fathom destiny♪

00:06:09.900 --> 00:06:11.349
♪Where blossoms fall♪

00:06:11.373 --> 00:06:15.220
♪I'm glad the fragrance
in our hearts stays the same♪

00:06:16.100 --> 00:06:17.820
♪Youth slips away♪

00:06:17.900 --> 00:06:21.700
♪Just to wait for your
once-in-a-thousand-years glance♪

00:06:22.660 --> 00:06:25.820
♪Dreams wander back
to the old road where we met♪

00:06:26.439 --> 00:06:30.199
Do you still enjoy
this "Moonlit Neon Dress Dance" of me?

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:31.498
♪Time rests upon the strings♪

00:06:31.522 --> 00:06:35.408
♪Waiting for someone
to brew a pot of tea♪

00:06:42.959 --> 00:06:44.800
If you remove all your adornments,

00:06:45.759 --> 00:06:47.079
I would like it even more.

00:06:50.439 --> 00:06:51.399
I

00:06:51.519 --> 00:06:53.720
have ways to make you
like it even more, Your Lordship.

00:06:59.839 --> 00:07:00.720
You misunderstand.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.040
What I mean is,

00:07:03.600 --> 00:07:05.240
I want you to confess honestly

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.399
for what purpose did you infiltrate
the Governor's Residence?

00:07:19.959 --> 00:07:22.319
Naturally, I hoped
to receive your favor.

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:28.279
Unwilling to tell the truth?

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:31.399
Then drink this cup of liquor.

00:07:37.639 --> 00:07:39.439
(Xiao Huaijin once gave me
poisoned liquor.)

00:07:42.500 --> 00:07:43.990
Your Lordship, please calm your anger.

00:07:44.380 --> 00:07:46.260
The matter of Shen Changning
being poisoned to death

00:07:46.279 --> 00:07:47.300
has nothing to do with me.

00:07:50.100 --> 00:07:51.279
A confession without pressure.

00:07:52.319 --> 00:07:53.759
When did I ever say

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:55.920
that Shen Changning died from poisoning?

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:00.279
Report, Your Lordship.

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:02.660
The Young Lord Xiao
has brought soldiers.

00:08:02.670 --> 00:08:04.130
He has already entered the residence.

00:08:11.850 --> 00:08:13.425
(Keep one's abilities in reserve)

00:08:14.587 --> 00:08:21.187
(Keep one's abilities in reserve)

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:24.720
I wonder under whose orders

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:27.199
Young Lord Xiao dares
to break into my residence.

00:08:27.519 --> 00:08:28.279
Governor Pei,

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:30.839
I do not wish to do this either.

00:08:31.212 --> 00:08:33.025
But His Majesty's birthday is near,

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.240
yet rumors say

00:08:34.480 --> 00:08:35.679
that within your residence,

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:38.600
there are items disrespectful
to His Majesty.

00:08:38.879 --> 00:08:41.519
Thus His Majesty ordered me

00:08:41.879 --> 00:08:44.039
to come and clear your name.

00:08:54.559 --> 00:08:56.080
Search thoroughly!

00:08:56.480 --> 00:08:57.240
Today,

00:08:58.919 --> 00:09:01.000
we must give His Majesty an explanation.

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:01.639
Yes.

00:09:07.679 --> 00:09:08.480
Governor Pei,

00:09:08.639 --> 00:09:11.519
they say the birthday star lives
a long life,

00:09:11.519 --> 00:09:12.559
ascending to immortality.

00:09:12.950 --> 00:09:14.950
How could you use talisman paper
to suppress evil?

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:16.000
Are you not afraid

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:18.840
that ill-intentioned people
will spread rumors,

00:09:20.159 --> 00:09:22.600
claiming you cursed
His Majesty's ascension?

00:09:23.512 --> 00:09:25.650
(Keep one's abilities in reserve)

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:30.399
Yellow background and red lines

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:32.600
can be used for cursing and suppression,

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:34.840
or for blessings and auspice.

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:42.559
How does Young Lord Xiao know

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:45.559
that the yellow-red lines
on the birthday talisman

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:48.720
were not meant as blessings
for His Majesty?

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:15.720
(Xiao Huaijin.)

00:10:16.559 --> 00:10:18.080
(You poisoned me.)

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:20.759
(I will personally put you to death.)

00:10:33.560 --> 00:10:35.720
The Governor sought out Taoist masters
across the land,

00:10:35.900 --> 00:10:37.759
and finally invited
the Grand Master of Heaven's Way

00:10:37.759 --> 00:10:39.480
to draw talismans and
pray for His Majesty.

00:10:39.799 --> 00:10:41.200
The cinnabar used in the talisman

00:10:41.210 --> 00:10:43.279
was refined with the Governor's
own fingertip blood

00:10:43.279 --> 00:10:44.759
to complete the ritual.

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:49.480
Whether it's curse or blessing,

00:10:49.919 --> 00:10:52.080
should be judged by
the Astronomical Bureau.

00:10:53.639 --> 00:10:55.240
Governor Pei,

00:10:55.919 --> 00:10:57.279
please come with me.

00:11:03.159 --> 00:11:04.080
Your Majesty,

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:05.679
I have verified without error.

00:11:06.039 --> 00:11:08.039
The secret text written
on the talisman paper

00:11:08.039 --> 00:11:09.240
is an ancient script,

00:11:09.240 --> 00:11:11.000
all of which are words of blessing.

00:11:11.062 --> 00:11:12.212
(The Emperor of Great Liang)

00:11:16.120 --> 00:11:16.919
Lord Lu,

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.799
you must look carefully.

00:11:18.799 --> 00:11:19.960
Arts of cursing

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:21.120
can mislead the people.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:22.720
This concerns not only

00:11:22.799 --> 00:11:24.320
Governor Pei's future,

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:26.960
but also the honor of the royal family.

00:11:26.960 --> 00:11:28.399
Young Lord Xiao, are you suggesting

00:11:28.900 --> 00:11:30.679
that I colluded
with the Astronomical Bureau

00:11:31.039 --> 00:11:32.360
to harm His Majesty?

00:11:33.039 --> 00:11:35.039
It is Governor Pei's actions

00:11:35.039 --> 00:11:36.879
that inevitably raise suspicion.

00:11:37.840 --> 00:11:40.440
Qilin Guards obey His Majesty's
command, guarding the capital,

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:41.759
watching over the realm.

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:44.440
As for these curse arts

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:47.240
and charlatans pretending
to wield mystic powers,

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:49.279
the Qilin Guards have executed
countless of them.

00:11:49.519 --> 00:11:50.120
Governor Pei...

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:50.799
- Enough.
- Your…

00:11:52.799 --> 00:11:53.440
Mr. Xiao,

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:55.120
I sent a verbal decree for you

00:11:55.960 --> 00:11:57.480
to clarify matters,

00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:59.919
not to let others misunderstand Mr. Pei.

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:02.320
Mr. Pei has rendered service
to the nation.

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:02.960
I

00:12:03.159 --> 00:12:04.519
have never doubted him.

00:12:05.759 --> 00:12:06.799
Your Majesty is wise.

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:08.000
I

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.720
was merely worried for Your Majesty

00:12:09.720 --> 00:12:11.240
and lost my composure for a moment.

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:13.240
I beg Your Majesty's punishment.

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:15.120
Mr. Pei.

00:12:15.559 --> 00:12:17.279
Mr. Xiao spoke rashly.

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:18.639
In your opinion,

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:20.320
how should he be punished?

00:12:24.039 --> 00:12:25.600
Though the Young Lord Xiao acted rashly,

00:12:26.039 --> 00:12:27.690
his loyalty to the court
is unquestioned.

00:12:29.919 --> 00:12:30.639
In my view,

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:33.200
half a month of seclusion for reflection

00:12:33.450 --> 00:12:34.600
will allow him to understand

00:12:34.759 --> 00:12:36.879
how he should serve
the court henceforth.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:40.679
Very well.

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:43.080
Mr. Xiao,

00:12:43.759 --> 00:12:44.960
thank Mr. Pei at once.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.200
Thank you, Mr. Pei,

00:12:53.759 --> 00:12:54.960
for showing mercy.

00:13:04.412 --> 00:13:06.250
(The Governor's Residence)

00:13:10.919 --> 00:13:11.480
Wretch!

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:17.639
Well?

00:13:18.200 --> 00:13:19.800
Nothing serious happened, right?

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:20.919
Wretch.

00:13:21.039 --> 00:13:21.960
Best beat her to death.

00:13:23.410 --> 00:13:25.879
A filthy brat from the brothel,
daring to use such vile tricks

00:13:25.879 --> 00:13:27.639
to seduce the Governor in his residence.

00:13:27.639 --> 00:13:28.960
Today, on the Madame's behalf,

00:13:28.960 --> 00:13:30.080
I'll teach you proper rules!

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:42.679
We are both women,

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:45.559
why tear each other apart
and serve as tools for others?

00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:48.200
Who is as shameless as you?

00:13:49.519 --> 00:13:50.120
Your Lordship.

00:14:00.759 --> 00:14:02.159
All of you, listen carefully.

00:14:02.879 --> 00:14:04.000
I, Xi Yan, have a bad temper

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:04.790
and a ruthless hand.

00:14:05.360 --> 00:14:06.500
If you wish to provoke me,

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:08.120
measure your own worth first.

00:14:25.879 --> 00:14:27.799
Someone capable of drawing Daoist seals

00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:30.960
reduced to a dancer
in the Governor's Residence?

00:14:31.399 --> 00:14:32.960
Your Lordship, do not laugh.

00:14:33.759 --> 00:14:35.480
I'm cleaning up your mess.

00:14:36.399 --> 00:14:37.320
Your beauty

00:14:37.639 --> 00:14:39.399
is far more vicious than I expected.

00:14:47.360 --> 00:14:48.840
(Her words and actions)

00:14:49.799 --> 00:14:51.240
(are completely unlike the woman)

00:14:51.240 --> 00:14:52.679
(I once saw in Xichun House.)

00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:55.360
(Who is she, truly?)

00:14:57.875 --> 00:14:59.875
